Let $E_{/F}$ be an elliptic curve and $p$ an odd prime such that $F(E_{p^\infty})$ is a pro-$p$ extension of $F$. Then, the following conditions are equivalent
\begin{enumerate}
    \item Conjecture \ref{CS conj} is valid, i.e., $\operatorname{Sel}_{p^\infty}^0(F_\infty, E)$ is cofinitely generated as a $\mathbb{Z}_p$-module. 
    \item The classical Iwasawa $\mu$-invariant $\mu_p(F)$ vanishes.
\end{enumerate}

